section.text:

Section 408 of the Food for Peace Act (
  7 U.S.C. 1736b
) shall be applied by substituting the date specified in section 106 of this joint resolution for December 31, 2012.


Section 810 of the Federal Lands Recreation Enhancement Act (
  16 U.S.C. 6809
) shall be applied by substituting 11 years for 10 years.

The authority provided by section 347 of the Department of the Interior and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 1999 (as contained in section 101(e) of division A of Public Law 105–277
        ; 
          16 U.S.C. 2104 note) shall continue in effect through the date specified in section 106 of this joint resolution.

